Sustaining Shadow												KEY:Shadowcaster ~ Sustaining Shadow				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ShadowcasterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																	DESC:When you reach 5th level, your bond to the Plane of Shadow allows you to absorb dark energies, mitigating certain biological needs. You need eat only a single meal per week to maintain health. At 10th level, you only need 1 hour of sleep per night (but you must still rest for 8 hours to regain your mysteries for the next day). At 15th level, you gain immunity to nonmagical diseases and poisons. Finally, at 20th level, you no longer need to breathe, and need never eat or sleep.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.113

